stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> TypeMessage
    TypeMessage --> SendMessage
    SendMessage --> DetectIntent
    DetectIntent --> IsGreeting : Hello/Hi/Hey
    DetectIntent --> IsThanks : Thank you
    DetectIntent --> IsJoke : Tell me a joke
    DetectIntent --> IsFrustration : Help/confused
    IsGreeting --> RandomGreetingResponse
    IsThanks --> ThankYouResponse
    IsJoke --> RandomJokeResponse
    IsFrustration --> HelpfulResponse
    RandomGreetingResponse --> DisplayResponse
    ThankYouResponse --> DisplayResponse
    RandomJokeResponse --> DisplayResponse
    HelpfulResponse --> DisplayResponse
    DisplayResponse --> TypeMessage
    DisplayResponse --> [*]